        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Sports Injuries</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Athletic strains, sprains, and overuse</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Electroacupuncture Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-6">Electroacupuncture</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Electroacupuncture uses traditional acupuncture combined with a gentle electric current to enhance the therapeutic effect. The electrical stimulation strengthens the muscle twitch response and improves results beyond acupuncture alone.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The electrical pulses are similar to transcutaneous electrical nerve stimulation (TENS) but act deeper and closer to the problem area. The current is low enough to cause a gentle twitch of the affected muscle fibers while preventing muscle spasm.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Benefits of Electroacupuncture</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Enhanced muscle relaxation
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Deeper tissue penetration
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
